      "content": "idk it just felt way more sudden than a normal headache. like it was 0 to 100 instantly. i have a big exam tomorrow so i really dont want to go to the doctor if i dont have to, doctors always make everything sound worse than it is. u think it's okay if i just take a couple of extra pills to make sure the fog goes away? like can i take like 1000mg of ibuprofen at once to just knock it out?",
